					<h1 class="text-center color-black">
						GET FOOD FAST &mdash; NOT FAST FOOD.
					</h1>
					<p class="text-center">
						Hello, we’re <strong>TOMATO RESTAURANT</strong>, your new premium food delivery service. We know
